Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:37.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:37.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:39.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:39.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
